                    </div>
                    <span>What is most disturbing about Crews is his intellectual dishonesty in setting up "straw men", especially early ideas of Freud's that Freud himself later modified -- as Crews well knows. (However, it is  possible that Crews is less dishonest than I believe, and merely ignorant.)</span>
                  
              
